productBaseInfoV1.title: Symphony Diet 22i Tower Air Cooler
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Does the thought of having stale air circulating in your house prevent you from installing an AC? While a ceiling fan alone is not enough in summer, this Symphony air cooler will make summer in your house less hotter and will also ensure that you are breathing fresh air. With a high-efficiency honeycomb cooling pad and a powerful blower, this cooler works on evaporative cooling technology, thus absorbing heat by evaporating water so the air circulated in your house is fresh and pure. Water Tank With A Capacity Of 22 Liters The water tank in this air cooler has a capacity of 22 liters, so you can enjoy uninterrupted cooling. The water tank also has an alarm that beeps to remind you when the water level is low. The pump gets turned off when the water level is low, thus preventing any damage to your air cooler. The drain plug at the bottom lets you remove residual water from the water tank. Dura-Pump Technology This cooler is designed with the Dura-Pump technology, making the water pump strong and durable, thus giving your air cooler a long life. Works On Inverter Power Frequent power cuts are not going to leave you sweating and irritable in your house as this Symphony air cooler also works on inverter power. Powerful Air Throw This air cooler has a powerful blower with an auto swing function, giving you a superior multi-directional air throw. You can modify the level of air throw by using the adjustable vertical louver. Includes Mosquito Net And Dust Filter With a mosquito net and a dust filter, the cooler ensures that the air that enters your house is fresh and hygienic. Ideal For Outdoor And Indoor Use With your Symphony tower air cooler, you can enjoy summer mornings in your garden, basking in fresh air as you relax on your hammock. Includes A Remote Control The cooler comes with a remote control so you can operate it without having to get up from the couch. The cooler also has a dock on which you can place the remote to look neat when you leave the house.

productBaseInfoV1.title: Singer Atlantic Mini Personal Air Cooler
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Those months of April and May are the hardest to bear with. However, with this air cooler from Singer, summer is no longer going to be so punishing. Designed with horizontal louvers, this air cooler has a stylish front and will look very cool in your office, shop or living room. Large Water Tank This air cooler has a large water tank with a capacity of 20 liters, letting you enjoy uninterrupted cooling for long hours. Large Cooling Area Of 250 Sq. Ft. This air cooler can cool an area of up to 250 square feet, which makes it ideal for homes, shops and offices. Motorized Vertical Louvers Movement The louvers in this air cooler have a motorized vertical movement, thus keeping your entire room cool. Inverter Compatible Frequent power cuts on hot summer days are not going to be a problem as this Singer Atlantic Mini air cooler even works on inverter power. Honeycomb Cooling Pads Built with a honeycomb pad, this air cooler mixes air and water in an optimum way to give you maximum cooling and is highly reliable. Drain Plug For Easy Cleaning The drain plug in this air cooler lets you drain the water easily if you want to get the air cooler refilled with clean water or if you accidentally filled a little too much water in the air cooler. Water Level Window With the water level window, you can easily see the level of water in the air cooler, so you can get it refilled in time, thus preventing any issues. Castor Wheels For Easy Portability With castor wheels, this air cooler is easy to roll so you can easily shift it from one room to another without any struggle.

productBaseInfoV1.title: Symphony Diet 50i Tower Air Cooler
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: The scorching heat of the sun can cause you grave discomfort. You really cannot do much about it, but you can definitely make your home more comfortable. If you are thinking how? It is as easy as investing in an air cooler such as this one from Symphony. Performance Designed to operate at 170W of power and with a 50L water capacity, this air cooler is energy-efficient and ensures cool breeze throughout the room. It features high-efficiency honeycomb pad and ice chamber which ensure effective and enhanced cooling in your home. Powerful and Durable The air cooler features a powerful blower and empty tank alarm which alerts you whenever there is no water in the air cooler. With the Dura-pump technology, you can be sure of the durability of the pump. Restore Function The System Restore function of the air cooler remembers and restores the previous settings. This air cooler works on inverter power and can be used both indoor and outdoor. It also comes with a fully functional remote control that makes operating it very easy.
